AQ-SPEC Staff at the South Coast AQMD

Source: vignettes/articles/DataFlowChart.Rmd
DataFlowChart.Rmd

Overview

The flow chart below illustrates how the AirSensor package can be used to download, process, and analyze data from PurpleAir sensors. Additionally, key functions associated with each step are listed demonstrating how they may be applied to transform “raw” data into fully processed data. Note, not every function available in the AirSensor package is included in this diagram.



Note: This diagram was developed based on the functionalities available in the AirSensor package version 0.5.17.
